biography: Caio holds a PhD in Computer Science and has been working with data and AI both in academia and industry since 2014. Currently working as a DS/MLE Consultant at Xebia Data, he is particularly keen on neural networks in its many forms and applications. His enthusiasm even led him to make a neural network fit inside a business card. With experience designing and taking applications into production, Caio has been recently focusing on how (Generative)AI can augment human productivity.
